    <style>
      /* initlogos style is here to prevent flashing */

      #os-logo {
        position: absolute;
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;

        background: #000 url('shared/resources/branding/initlogo.png') bottom right no-repeat;

        z-index: 65536;

        opacity: 1;
        transition: opacity 1s ease 2s;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      #carrier-logo {
        position: absolute;
        overflow: hidden;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: #000;
      }

      #carrier-logo &gt; img,
      #poweroff-splash &gt; img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: absolute;        
        opacity: 1;
        transition: opacity 1s ease 2s;
      }

      #carrier-logo &gt; video,
      #poweroff-splash &gt; video {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        position: absolute;        
        opacity: 1;
        transition: opacity 1s ease;
      }

      #carrier-logo.transparent {
        background: transparent;
      }

      #carrier-logo &gt; img.hide,
      #carrier-logo &gt; video.hide,
      #os-logo.hide,
      #poweroff-splash &gt; img.hide,
      #poweroff-splash &gt; video.hide {
        opacity: 0;
      }
    </style>
